{"tid":779572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利行車天橋崩塌　逾20車跌落地面釀22死","createTime":"2018-08-14T13:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T13:41:07.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7272d27b32a1150ace796698d05b34a3666d7ba8","tid":779572,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"意大利北部熱那亞市工業區的一條行車天橋於周二（14日）倒塌，當地傳媒估計崩塌的橋面長約200米。消防員接報到場，至少20輛汽車掉落地面，造成至少22死，8人受傷。有在場記者形容是「世界末日的場景」，目擊者驚慌尖叫。該國交通部長形容事件是「重大悲劇」。 <br />\n<br />\n事發時當地有狂風暴雨，警方初步懷疑崩塌的莫蘭迪大橋（Morandi Bridge）有結構問題，導致事故。消防部門已派逾200人到場救災，暫時從瓦礫中救起數名傷者，已由救援直升機送院，他們均受重傷。肇事路段崩塌後，瓦礫散滿一地，從現場相片可見，一輛綠色貨車停泊在崩塌口，相信司機及時在橋身倒塌時停車，貨車才沒有跌落地面。消防部門發言人表示，倒塌路段險些壓落附近的鐵道路軌。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，莫蘭迪大橋建於1960年代，當時是全歐洲首條斜拉混凝土橋，全長1.1公里，屬A10公路的一部分，曾於2016年進行維修。"},{"pid":"dd3ca507763c19b6d8d721ec0a6f42266f97fae0","tid":779572,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20180814/mobile/bkn-20180814182857495-0814_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20180814%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180814182857495-0814_00912_001.html&d=qhFynAJyl%2BPpBMIAlS%2FNtE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=97b2689e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20180814/mobile/bkn-20180814182857495-0814_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6edd6bee066b6ceed6a9352330a8dbdbd76cf651","tid":779572,"uid":69380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"港G澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23736a6a50f60830bf34dc9f865390b8402dfd4","tid":779572,"uid":31744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"今日意大利 明白香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13187b282ef32c50de8f0d017823fab13a194935","tid":779572,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/212723_2af8c509a9c987dc3e9f6c3107d54248.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F212723_2af8c509a9c987dc3e9f6c3107d54248.png&h=7bd94d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d6c296787cc4ede16f6a951d4549c979bd5bb5a","tid":779572,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93977cc4d2a87ec5235f3d0ed1d30f2d10cbff4","tid":779572,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:41:07.000Z","msg":"意粉佬係懶"}]}